==播映==
2000年，探索頻道播映《解放鯊魚週》，節目由知名動物學家[[奈吉爾·馬文|奈吉爾·馬文]]主持。同年，探索頻道發放六百萬份{{link-en|普耳弗里希|Pulfrich effect}}實體鏡給位於美國與加拿大的觀眾，因節目在介紹史前巨鯊的橋段中包含3D畫面。<ref>[http://www.3dglassesonline.com/company/press/bartlett-manufacturer-swims-sharks-upcoming-3d-television-event Bartless Manufacturer “swims with sharks” in Upcoming 3D Television Event] {{Wayback|url=http://www.3dglassesonline.com/company/press/bartlett-manufacturer-swims-sharks-upcoming-3d-television-event |date=20101130090908 }}, 3dglassesonline.com, August 11, 2000.</ref>

2005年，探索頻道知名節目《[[流言終結者|流言終結者]]》的主持人[[亚当·萨维奇|亚当·萨维奇]]及[[杰米·海纳曼|杰米·海纳曼]]主持了該年的《鯊魚週》，節目首映為長達兩小時的《流言終結者之大白鯊特集》。

2006年，《[[幹盡苦差事|幹盡苦差事]]》主持人[[麥可·羅|麥可·羅]]擔起了主持人的任務，而節目中有兩集《幹盡苦差事》特集。同年，探索頻道在[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[银泉_(马里兰州)|銀泉]]的總部為了慶祝鯊魚週，在建築物的支架上搭了鯊魚頭及鯊魚尾巴，使得大廈看起來像條巨大的鯊魚。<ref name="cbslocal1">{{cite web|title=Return of "Chompie" In Silver Spring Building Marks 25th Anniversary of Shark Week|url=http://washington.cbslocal.com/2012/07/31/return-of-chompie-in-silver-spring-building-marks-25th-anniversary-of-shark-week/|accessdate=August 5, 2012|date=31 July 2012|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411022250/https://washington.cbslocal.com/2012/07/31/return-of-chompie-in-silver-spring-building-marks-25th-anniversary-of-shark-week/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2007年，探索頻道慶祝《鯊魚週二十週年》，並邀請[[现代鲁宾逊|现代鲁宾逊]]的主持人{{link-en|莱斯·史特劳|Les Stroud}}主持節目。

2008年的《鯊魚週》於7月27日首播，於8月2日結束，由《[[流言終結者|流言終結者]]》與[[麥可·羅|麥可·羅]]共同主持。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dsc.discovery.com/convergence/sharkweek/sharkweek.html |title=Shark Week 2008: Discovery Channel: Shark Behavior and Conservation |publisher=Dsc.discovery.com |date=2010-07-07 |accessdate=2012-09-20 |archive-date=2010-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100708214049/http://dsc.discovery.com/convergence/sharkweek/sharkweek.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Vino Crianza |url=http://www.lesstroudonline.com/blog/?p=37 |title=Les Stroud’s Blog ~ Survivorman » Les Stroud hosts “Surviving Sharks” for Shark Week 2008 |publisher=Les Stroud |date= |accessdate=2012-09-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090302082627/http://www.lesstroudonline.com/blog/?p=37 |archivedate=2009-03-02 }}</ref>該年首映為《[[流言終結者|流言終結者]]》的鯊魚特輯，並由《[[幹盡苦差事|幹盡苦差事]]》的鯊魚特輯接續播出。

2009年的《鯊魚週》於8月2日晚間首播。

2010年的《鯊魚週》由[[深夜秀_(愛爾蘭廣播電視節目)|深夜秀]]的[[克雷格·费格斯|克雷格·费格斯]]主持，於8月1日首播，並新推出六集鯊魚特集。<ref name="discovery1">{{cite web |url=http://dsc.discovery.com/tv/shark-week/tv-shows.html |title=SHARK WEEK: TV Shows: Discovery Channel |publisher=Dsc.discovery.com |date= |accessdate=2012-09-20 |archive-date=2012-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120922190519/http://dsc.discovery.com/tv/shark-week/tv-shows.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>探索頻道總部大樓再次裝上了鯊魚裝飾，這次甚至將牠取名，名叫「小咬牙」（{{lang|en|Chompie}}）<ref name="cbslocal1"/>該年的《鯊魚週》成為節目有史以來觀看人數最高的一次，一共有3080萬名觀眾。<ref>Source: Nielsen Media Research; cume; M-Su 8-11P; LSD P2+; 6-minute qualifier</ref>而《鯊魚週》也在當年成為歷史最悠久的有線電視活動。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/08/10/discovery-channels-23rd-annual-shark-week-is-most-watched-ever-seen-by-30-8-million-people/59634 |title=Discovery Channel's 23rd Annual 'Shark Week' Is Most-Watched Ever; Seen by 30.8 Million People |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.com |date=2010-08-10 |accessdate=2012-09-20 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>

2011年的《鯊魚週》於7月31日首播，由[[安迪·薩姆伯格|安迪·薩姆伯格]]主持，並包含七集特集。<ref name="discovery1"/>

2012年的《鯊魚週》由網路作家{{link-en|飛利浦·德佛朗哥|Philip DeFranco}}主持，於美國中部時間8月12日晚間8點首映。而這次「小咬牙」睽違了一年，重新被佈置在探索頻道總部大樓的支架上。<ref name="cbslocal1"/>為慶祝該節目的25週年，探索頻道開放觀眾透過[[Facebook|Facebook]]和[[Twitter|Twitter]]投票，決定節目最後的機械[[巨牙鯊|巨牙鯊]]會將哪項物品壓碎。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/06/27/25th-anniversary-of-shark-week-week-to-premiere-sunday-august-12-on-discovery/139585/|title=25th Anniversary of 'Shark Week Week' to Premiere Sunday August 12 on Discovery|publisher=TV By the Numbers|date=June 27, 2012|accessdate=June 27, 2012|archive-date=2021-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531013635/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/06/27/25th-anniversary-of-shark-week-week-to-premiere-sunday-august-12-on-discovery/139585/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2013的《鯊魚週》於8月4日星期日首映。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://vine.co/v/hB2juljV7ep |title=Discovery Channel's post on Vine |publisher=Vine.co |date= |accessdate=2013-06-28 |archive-date=2013-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130712110510/https://vine.co/v/hB2juljV7ep |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/06/28/shark-week-returns-to-discovery-channel-august-4-with-the-most-hours-of-shark-programming-ever/189592/ | title='Shark Week' Returns to Discovery Channel August 4 With the Most Hours of Shark Programming Ever | work=TV By the Numbers | accessdate=2013-06-28 | archive-date=2021-05-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531013014/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/06/28/shark-week-returns-to-discovery-channel-august-4-with-the-most-hours-of-shark-programming-ever/189592/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>該年首映為文獻電視片{{link-en|巨齒鯊大復活|Megalodon: The Monster Shark Lives}}，主要在探討若[[巨牙鯊|巨牙鯊]]存在現代，會對海洋產生什麼影響。<ref>Rich Juzwiak, "[http://gawker.com/shark-week-opens-with-fake-megalodon-documentary-1028053485 Shark Week Opens with Fake Megalodon Documentary] {{Wayback|url=http://gawker.com/shark-week-opens-with-fake-megalodon-documentary-1028053485 |date=20130808041048 }}", ''Gawker'', August 5, 2013.</ref>

